      "validationActivity": "Comparison of CFD pressure-rise predictions to experimental measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump benchmark dataset",
      "comparisonMetric": "Relative error in pressure rise (%)",
      "comparisonResult": "Mean relative error 6.4%; maximum relative error 14.2% at low-flow operating point"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vad-hemolysis-index-validation",
